 26th March 1917 . Woke at 8 for duti till 12 . Came on again at 8 till 12 midnight . Veri quiet day . Cold with sleet shower . 27th March 1917 . Got up at 8 for duti till 12 . Came off went for dinner . Read slept dure afternoon . Had tea at estaminet Went on again at 6 till 8. Got to sleep at 9.30 . 28th March 1917 . Went on at 4 till 8 this morn . Fool around after get fix up round the joint . Came on again at 4 till 6 . Did the shift of 12 till 4 at night . 29th March 1917 . Got up at 10.30 this morn . Came on again at 12 till 4 . Fritz shell the Pont Niepp Road tonight . Went on duti again at 8 till 12 . 30th March 1917 . Got up at 8. After breakfast went down to the trench to look round for week OP work . Came back for dinner then went down again did duti at the Steel Tree and OP. Came back to HQrs fix up for the night where I sleep. 31st March 1917 . Got up at 8 and woke offic . Left trench at 9.30 for Batteri . Veri hungri . Had breakfast and clean up after dinner fool around new quarter . This OP job mean a full night 's rest everi night so it not too bad . Walk down again to trench tonight for FOO 's report .
